 <p id="Par80" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">A VOLY of 2 years of per capita consumption is generally the same order of magnitude as empirical estimates based on willingness-to-pay surveys
  <span class="sup">
   <a ref-type="bibr" rid="CR21" href="#CR21">21</a>
  </span>, but we also test several alternative values in sensitivity analyses. Final (post-health) per capita consumption, 
  <span class="italic">c</span>
  <sub>
   <span class="italic">it</span>
  </sub> is calculated as:
