 <p id="Par81" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">With monetized aerosol impacts now included in the economic framework, RICE can follow its normal optimization procedure to find the decarbonization pathway that maximizes the objective (Eq. (
  <a rid="Equ1" ref-type="" href="#Equ1">1</a>)).
 </p>
